12794306082012121145.Text: All hail the new sheeftain of Thirshk! Becaushe of you, the mead hall ish open again! Here'sh to your health!

1256984149712316.Text: "In the cave she met the beast, and cut quite short its evil feast! And when the Udyrfrykte did fall, the chieftain came and claimed his hall!"

193547054475829552.Text: "In the cave he met the beast, and cut quite short its evil feast! And when the Udyrfrykte did fall, the chieftain came and claimed his hall!"

235771227094803517.Text: Be careful out here in the wild, friend. There's more roaming about than just wolves and bears.

60402783913321633.Text: Krr- AWWGH!  We can end your curse!  The wolf may walk no more!

24735214791899020629.Text: By the Gods, it's good to see you again!

234325771990717133.Text: By the Gods, not you!  Get out of my house, cur!

195835886491221891.Text: You there! Can you help a warrior in trouble?

1727420515115095649.Text: Did you see me? I fought like a wolf possessed! Ha!

52893038816431137.Text: Hello, friend. Have you met my love, Brandr?

28121188981523628759.Text: I'd like you to meet Erna. We have a love my wife would never understand.

891014071470913692.Text: The Rite of the Wolf Giver is nearly complete! He he he he he he he he he.

339129856224418382.Text: My sisters and I must make our brew before the Rite can proceed.

258049231513813829.Text: With the proper ingredients, we can cure your lycanthropy, yes....

12253205622678411176.Text: Wolfsbane, belladonna, and the purity of innocence are what we need. He he he he he he he.

6804143281430127152.Text: Yaawwwnnn!  Inside, outside, I'll sleep anywhere.

2677424690294586587.Text: Yawwwwwnn! Hello again my friend. Thanks to you, I can sleep again. Yawwwnnn.....

1763019496141908149.Text: Behold the sea, friend. Never will you meet a maiden so beautiful...or unforgiving.

6787158202142225603.Text: My lord, I can craft armor worthy of a chieftain!

1982727632099012913.Text: Did you see the size of that beast!

523114323269029757.Text: Come, friend! I make the best armor on all of Solstheim.

302631425188925509.Text: Candy, candy -- he makes so much! Uncle Sweetshare has a magic touch! So it's back to the workshop in the snow! With lovely lanterns all aglow! He he! Ha ho! He he he ha ha ho!

519124701175217185.Text: Well now, if you're not the comeliest lass I've ever laid eyes on. Come here, and let Big Erich keep you warm.

2807300764708564.Text: Keep your distance, friend, if you want to keep your head.

1198359172836425410.Text: Thish is the besht mead hall anywhere, friend. You'll not find better in Shkyrim itshelf.

5936917927707931.Text: Welcome to Thirsk, friend! You should speak to Skjoldr Wolf-Runner. He is the chieftain of this hall, and wishes to meet all new arrivals.

30513231273074612964.Text: Our mead ish the nectar of Shor himshelf, imported all the way from Shkyrim!

290872225213372693.Text: All hail the chieftain of Thirsk! Slayer of the Udyrfrykte! May the mead flow forever!

18995306523063670.Text: Thirsk is closed, and without a chieftain. These are sad times.

4117169342999321614.Text: Watch yourself near Erich, friend.  He's a swine of a man.  It's too bad he's my clan brother....

24407293992122021839.Text: Have you found it? Have you found the entrance to Sovngarde?

15873433824111438.Text: Our dark business is complete. Erna is dead! Hahahahahahahaha!

7495242412720613344.Text: My husband is mine, do you understand me? Mine! That harlot Erna will pay!

718208892910616454.Text: Oddfrid tells me things, friend. Secret things.

16518234015818361.Text: They've taken my Oddfrid. My sweet, dear Oddfrid....

3685290651284420171.Text: The forces of darkness are mine to command! All shall bow before the terrible power of Tymvaul the Dark!

3005420150319505488.Text: My son.... My poor son.... Please, please help a sad old man.

2656331469413423592.Text: The creatures have gone, and the lands are whole. Surely the All-Maker is pleased.

88162600726978799.Text: The Ristaag is complete. Praise be to the All-Maker.

1327476691554731527.Text: Greetings, Blodskaal. You and I must speak of the Ristaag.

1737630156257491541.Text: You are not welcome here while you follow the path of the beast.

3099267392146519194.Text: I know you have been infected by these werewolves.

5925285081832111156.Text: I've only just arrived, and to this horror.

1299214529132521205.Text: Travel back to the Skaal village. I will meet you there soon.

134942162393626352.Text: Ah...you've arrived. These are strange times, my friend.

1739631475957823339.Text: Hello again, friend. What may I do for you?

24245298792039923720.Text: You were to perform the Ritual of the Gifts. I hope your way has been easy.

178891993033261868.Text: Greetings to you, wanderer. Why have you returned to our village?

2916517714270631329.Text: You have returned. I would hear of your journey.

2084324280176055447.Text: What can this smith do for you? Armor, weapons? Some conversation?

19096176362409917010.Text: I have nothing to say. My time is done.

262463066334052756.Text: You know my crime. Get on with your job.

1414894433700274.Text: Yes? I understand you are investigating Engar Ice-Mane's theft.

2338630149427920363.Text: You have cleared my husband's name. What can I do for you?

1447232171280629639.Text: You are the one who is to investigate a crime that has been blamed on my husband. How may I help you?

30061204231823631853.Text: No time for talk. The Hunt has begun!

247847370102526762.Text: Let us fight through to the end.

14274109301695225357.Text: This place! It is fit for a warrior like Heart-Fang!

2417135211879417123.Text: You've returned from the lake! I trust you completed your task.

247832014834818667.Text: You are to prove your strength as a warrior of the Skaal.

253320298499223706.Text: You have done well, showing your loyalty and wisdom

5189437221986955.Text: You were to investigate a crime. Have you done this?

205815768135704740.Text: You have shown your loyalty to the Skaal.

13338237781868830296.Text: You were told to perform the rituals needed to restore the power of the Skaal. What have you done?

12109247951228018206.Text: I was trying to explain to you, outlander, that you have much to atone for.

27338101851888414694.Text: What do you want, stranger? Why are you among the Skaal?

395533641107511079.Text: There is no more to say to you, stranger. The Skaal wish you no harm, but you are not welcome here.

2508451653046026720.Text: You've returned to our village, outlander. What is your business here?

6304545325813013.Text: What can Long-Tooth do for you?

53696501651623088.Text: The Spirit Bear is dead, and the Ristaag is nearly complete.

21778224632136511968.Text: You and I must continue the Ristaag.

1988531525327642472.Text: Shhh...we must hunt carefully and quietly. There is no time to talk.

9468289082706916707.Text: Come back at nightfall, my friend. We will perform the Ristaag.

1664622050128032653.Text: Greetings, Blodskaal. Korst Wind-Eye has told me much about you.

5149413463721696.Text: Stay with Long-Tooth, Blodskaal. The Ristaag must be completed.

1864358711356726625.Text: We must complete the Ristaag. The All-Maker demands this.

4800225941948027787.Text: You have cleared my name and restored my honor. What can I do for you, my friend?

1803920886702419691.Text: You, who are to be my judge, what would you ask of me?

41322780289626877.Text: I am glad to see you alive!

1090223112734429209.Text: It is good to see you again, friend.

1396897612855526899.Text: I will wait here and defend this gate.

36506880309807004.Text: Be strong, my friend. You will persevere.

60621522532615976.Text: We must find our way through this maze.

23434244193158826517.Text: This place is not of this world. I fear for our lives.

28556164122138912496.Text: Have you found more information on the weapons being smuggled from the Fort?

1368105358624604.Text: I asked you to investigate why the morale has been low in the fort. Have you learned anything?

3099322991412830438.Text: Be strong, my friend. You will persevere.

21463325793924005.Text: This place is not of this world. I fear for our lives.

2109239401427432644.Text: Have you found more information on the weapons being smuggled from the Fort?

322652006353757131.Text: Just another of life's little disappointments...

1457456982281498.Text: Yes? What can I do for you? I am Captain Falx Carius, commander of Fort Frostmoth.

22773219561372718524.Text: Yes? What can this humble priest do for you?

3433297422397330672.Text: I got nothing more to say.

32016282653258710569.Text: You've got to find the Captain! The fort needs him!

1247419568193295603.Text: You're back. And just in time!

154910851493828697.Text: We gotta find these guys. And smash 'em. Smash 'em good.

973123591493612194.Text: Cap'n said you'd be by. I'm supposed to assist you with something?

15713171291941919557.Text: All is well here at Fort Frostmoth.

95085293067214145.Text: We must find Captain Carius. This place will fall to shambles without him.

26099952346724900.Text: Let us ferret out this ring of smugglers.

26928226011047512912.Text: Captain Carius mentioned that you might come to speak with me. How may I assist you?

193419224975110833.Text: I'll be gone soon. I promise you that.

68079003628822376.Text: Have you come for Stalhrim weapons, friend?

2974614991009311728.Text: You have no business being here, stranger. Leave now.

8881297679496870.Text: Have you come for Stalhrim armor, friend?

5838125493191428372.Text: We'll have no dealings with the likes of you. Begone.

161978476173073903.Text: Look, I said I'll leave. Just stay away from me, will you?

3972136657073449.Text: You'll not infect me with your Devilry! I am here to defend Nature, and I'll do so at any cost! Now begone!

247863170115331302.Text: You chose Falco. Fine. Just leaves more for me.

32403267601379426814.Text: Without me, it all falls to pieces.

1436731032519113049.Text: What they don't know won't hurt them.

67162902150293009.Text: The Company does well, we get rich, and everyone is happy.

2494388191467315202.Text: We'll whip this island into shape, and make it pay.

301224654487827407.Text: You scratch my back? I'll scratch yours.

1970359321840318696.Text: Time is money. Let's get moving here.

2021710248331516549.Text: Better. Just stick with it, and we'll all get rich.

296615719314755326.Text: Don't bother me with trivial details. Know what's important, and do it right the first time.

15888100542365219496.Text: I can't believe it. Can't anyone do anything right?

17515246263107226576.Text: Who cares about Nord crackpots? We got a lot to do here.

918514031212408694.Text: You're with Carnius now. I'm sorry, but it was your choice.

282742267384874510.Text: Well, it couldn't get worse... Could it?

14030178902374718071.Text: If it's not one thing, it's another.

71285934208583356.Text: Don't know what I'd do without you.

20980279132211719744.Text: Between us, we just might pull this off.

254112604474827008.Text: YOU'RE not the problem. You're doing fine... thank the Gods.

1401022602247195821.Text: Okay. The supply ship is fine. What else can go wrong?

17020296392187530479.Text: Decisions are good. But good decisions are better.

23389175832240019174.Text: Too bad about the ship. Not your fault, though.

3253914610130331280.Text: Hroldar is gone, but we have other problems.

269328922166146170.Text: Good work with the ebony. Keep it up.

6565149881179714882.Text: Hello! Are you here on assignment, or did you just stop by?

32573182191260510819.Text: So, Carnius talked you into joining this little venture, did he?

19256932439831048.Text: I'm sorry, but I'm here on official business, and I don't have time to chat.

309631640110117302.Text: I.... I'm taking care of the supplies. Just keep your distance, all right?

291333141130719427.Text: Well now. Have they finally sent someone to deliver the extra payment I requested?

1295735702634320896.Text: Well, if it isn't you again. I daresay you're one of the nicest people I met, and that's saying quite a lot.

221343057432522113.Text: Get them away, get them away! The horrid things!

885713103265735503.Text: Raven Rock, the jewel of Solstheim.... For whatever that's worth.

2555529360313783763.Text: Another day, another hundred piles of ore.

2860115062247169617.Text: Another day, another hundred piles of ore.

3188185403198316695.Text: My lungs must be as black as these rocks by now.

2128523207214310328.Text: May your ore be pure, and your profits large.

318603227611944221.Text: Please do something about my poor husband!

48801173253581836.Text: Uh... there's a perfectly good explanation for this, I assure you...

2996827968729815400.Text: May your ore be pure, and your profits large.

29813176791022736.Text: The company's work is never done, friend.

830931774684826307.Text: This place isn't much, but I've forged the best of weapons with less.

24603557332122878.Text: Here to choose from our incredibly limited selection? What'll it be?
